[quote=“pickledegg, post:47, topic:43309”]i need a coder here is some work if you like

i need code for monsters everywere in free world were the monsters normally are in runescape
after cutting tree, the tree stays it must be gone for a sec like in the real one
if i use bow i just hit him with my hand
cant eat food
cant mine
cant melt ores into bars
ruins dont teleport me too runecrafting place

this are problems can u fix them for me?[/quote]
Maybe I can help. You need to learn how to make “use” function.
It’s like this:

if (objectID == ID){ do something blah blah. }
The ID is the object’s ID for example 11616 is a wooden door. If you clicl on it, it activates this script.
the “do something blah blah” is the part what exactly it does for example you can make “additem(itemID,amount);”
You can also add messages when doing it, for example:

sendMessage("You pick the flax");

I hope you know where do these codes go, but if not, then search for “If (objectID ==” in your client.java

Hope i could help:)
